Set Up and Manage CRM Analytics on Mobile

Optimize dashboard layouts for mobile devices, and administer CRM Analytics for mobile.

Access Data When You’re Offline
View and analyze data on your mobile device when internet access isn’t available.

Generate Unique CRM Analytics Dashboard Layouts for Different Devices
After you add widgets to a dashboard, optimize it for viewing on smaller screens.

Connected App for CRM Analytics on Mobile
Install the CRM Analytics App Package to allow your mobile clients to easily connect to your org.

Connected App for Wave Web
Use the Wave Web App Package when you want to manage how web clients like mobile browsers and apps display CRM Analytics content.

Enable CRM Analytics App Push Notifications
Push notifications let your users know when their data conditions have been met.

Customize CRM Analytics for iOS using Mobile SDK
Set custom login servers and manage access to settings on CRM Analytics for iOS.

Launch CRM Analytics Assets with URLs
The CRM Analytics mobile app supports deep linking URL schemes, which allow a user to launch the app from a third-party or web application.
